NK039(ti)025:0: badz+ra pa ni la na mo /
NK039(ti)025:1: dam sri lte phur nag mo'i mnan pa /
NK039(ti)025:2: de yang sngon dang po lha mo chu srin gyi
NK039(ti)025:3: rgyal po ku be ra gnyis sbyor ba byas pas
NK039(ti)025:4: bu mo lte phur nag mo byung ste /
NK039(ti)025:5: de ma mnan na bsgrub pa po la gnod pa'i /
NK039(ti)025:6: mnan thabs shog bu la bud med kyi gzugs bris /
NK039(ti)025:7: rkang pa bya rkang 'dra ba'i bris pa'i snying gar /
NK039(ti)025:8: tshe dang longs spyod la bar du gcod pa'i dam
NK039(ti)025:9: sri lte phur nag mo ma ra y+aa dzahdzah bdud
NK039(ti)025:10: mo ma r+aa ya dzahnanah bya ba bris mthar dza'i
NK039(ti)025:11: bskor / de nas mdun du gru gsum mtho gang ba'i nang du bzhag /
NK039(ti)025:12: bdag phyag na rdo rje bsgom la /
NK039(ti)025:13: de ni dam sri nag mo gang bris pa ltar
NK039(ti)025:14: du bskyed las thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pa'i
NK039(ti)025:15: sprul pa'i tshogs spros pas bkug la bstim /
NK039(ti)025:16: phur pa phyag na rdo rje bskyed la btab shing gzir bar bsam /
NK039(ti)025:17: de nas rta nag gi rnyid pa la dza bris /
NK039(ti)025:18: badz+ra tsan+di ma ha ro sha na h'u phatah tshe
NK039(ti)025:19: dang longs spyod dngos grub la bar du gcod par
NK039(ti)025:20: byed pa'am / dam sri lte phur nag mo'i srog
NK039(ti)025:21: la m+aa ra y+aa dzah bdud mo ma ra ya
NK039(ti)025:22: nanah yi dam sngags gsham du bsgrub /
NK039(ti)025:25: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du yi ge khangahnaga po yongs su gyur pa las /
NK039(ti)025:26: gnam lcags kyi khang sgrom nag po nang gru gsum
NK039(ti)025:27: dmar nag tu 'dug pa kha khyer bang rim gsum
NK039(ti)025:28: dang ldan pa bang rim dang po la bya shan
NK039(ti)025:30: bar ma la gcan gzan mang po rgyug pa /
NK039(ti)025:31: 'og ma na mi ro dang rta ro mi khrag dang rta khrag 'khyil ba /
NK039(ti)025:32: de'i dbus su yi ge tri yongs su gyur pa
NK039(ti)025:33: las dam sri bya mchu can mgon skyabs med pa
NK039(ti)025:34: sngo ba skya ba 'dar 'khri li li byed pa
NK039(ti)025:35: / kha nas smre sngags dang 'o dod 'bod pa /
NK039(ti)025:36: yan lag bzhi sgrogs su bcug pa gcig tu gyur /
NK039(ti)025:37: 'gug gzhug lan gsum gang rung bya /
NK039(ti)025:39: ya ma dam sri 'gab 'dre ma ra ya dzahdzahnanahnanah
NK039(ti)025:40: dre'u ya ma sha khug nanah bsngo rak+mo ku ru
NK039(ti)025:41: ko tri tsan+da dam sri sha ra gnod byed 'gab
NK039(ti)025:42: 'dre dam sri gnod pa thams cad ma ra ya
NK039(ti)025:44: rdo leb la rdo rje rgya gram bris la mnan /
NK039(ti)025:45: thun mtshams su sngar bzhin bya /
NK039(ti)025:47: mchod rten rnying pa'i 'og gam lam rgya gram du mnan /
NK039(ti)025:48: de nas dam sri ldang mi nus so //
NK039(ti)025:49: mnan pa'i dus su 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)025:50: h'uh nyon cig dam sri pho mo nyon //
NK039(ti)025:51: nga ni dpal chen gsang ba'i bdag /
NK039(ti)025:53: nga'i bka' la mi gnas med //
NK039(ti)025:54: dam sri pho mo bya ba khyod //
NK039(ti)025:55: gsang sngags dam tshig nyams pa yis //
NK039(ti)025:56: dreg pa pho mo rtsis chos kyi //
NK039(ti)025:57: bdud mo nag mo gnod sbyin mo //
NK039(ti)025:58: las kyi dbang gi skyes pa te //
NK039(ti)025:59: dgra bo'i gra tshogs 'dus pa lags //
NK039(ti)025:60: bsgrub la bar du gcod pa dang //
NK039(ti)025:61: rnal 'byor pho mo gsang ba dang /
NK039(ti)025:62: lus ngag yid gsum dbang bsdud byed //
NK039(ti)025:63: myur mgyogs rdzu 'phrul glog gi dbang //
NK039(ti)025:64: bya yi mgo la mi yi lus //
NK039(ti)025:65: rlung gi rkang la skar chen mig /
NK039(ti)025:66: spu gris so la mi zin pa //
NK039(ti)025:67: rnal 'byor rnams la gnod byed pa /
NK039(ti)025:69: chad dam bka' las mi 'da' bar //
NK039(ti)025:70: bsgrub mchog rnams la bar ma gcod //
NK039(ti)025:71: bdag la gnod pa ma byed cig /
NK039(ti)025:72: dam rdzas gtor ma 'di longs la //
NK039(ti)025:73: bsgrub pa'i rdzas la 'dir ma rngams //
NK039(ti)025:74: gsang sngags dam tshig gnyen po yis //
NK039(ti)025:75: las rnams bsgrub las ma zin par //
NK039(ti)025:76: dabye'o dkar ro mtshams chod cig /
NK039(ti)025:77: dpag tshad brgyad khri'i ri rab 'og /
NK039(ti)025:78: mnan na ma ldang dam sri rnams //
NK039(ti)025:79: bskal pa 'di las man chad nas //
NK039(ti)025:80: ya yam rgyal mo bya ba dang //
NK039(ti)025:81: ma yam rgyal mo grul chen yod //
NK039(ti)025:82: dam sri pho mo der song zhig /
NK039(ti)025:84: lcags mkhar mun rib nang shed na //
NK039(ti)025:85: gshin rje'i rgyal po'i chos bshad 'dug /
NK039(ti)025:86: de'i drung du chos nyon cig /
NK039(ti)025:87: phyi mig yar la ma lta zhig /
NK039(ti)025:88: ri rab chen po'i 'og tu non //
NK039(ti)025:89: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting du 'phangs //
NK039(ti)025:90: bskal pa chen po grangs med du //
NK039(ti)025:91: sangs rgyas bstan pa ma rdzogs par //
NK039(ti)025:92: steng gi phyogs su ma ldang zhig /
NK039(ti)025:93: rdo rje rgya gram h'u bcas kyi //
NK039(ti)025:94: mnan no dam sri pho mo mnan //
NK039(ti)025:95: bskal pa'i bar du ma ldang zhig /
NK039(ti)025:96: chos spyod thams cad la bar du gdon ngan pho mo /
NK039(ti)025:98: dam sri pho mo rnyab pa lag ring btsan yam shud dmar po /
NK039(ti)025:99: the'u rang stong 'khrugs dam sri lte phur nag mo ma ra ya nan /
NK039(ti)025:103: kha tam ma ra ya nan /
NK039(ti)025:105: dmar gtor gcig rgyab rdo rje rgya gram gyis kha gcod /
NK039(ti)025:107: las kyi rjes mi mngon pa bya /
NK039(ti)025:109: rang phyag na rdo rje'i gur khang bskyed /
NK039(ti)025:110: de ltar byas na dam sri mi ldong bar 'gyur ro //
NK039(ti)025:112: slob dpon bee ro tsa na /
NK039(ti)025:114: bla ma drag po lo ts+aa ba rje btsun rin spur ldan /
NK039(ti)025:115: ma ra tsa shes rab rdo rje /
NK039(ti)025:118: rje btsun re d+ha ba la rim bzhin du rgyud pa'i shin tu kho na yin pa'i gsang rgya /
